 148:Core/Src/mpu6050.c ****   /**
 149:Core/Src/mpu6050.c ****    * Online bias recalibration — call ONLY when robot is stationary!
 150:Core/Src/mpu6050.c ****    * Uses exponential moving average to slowly adjust the gyro bias.
 151:Core/Src/mpu6050.c ****    * This compensates for thermal drift without blocking like full calibration.
 152:Core/Src/mpu6050.c ****    *
 153:Core/Src/mpu6050.c ****    * At 200 Hz with RECAL_ALPHA=0.001, time constant ≈ 5 seconds.
 154:Core/Src/mpu6050.c ****    * After ~10 seconds idle, bias is well-corrected for the current temperature.
 155:Core/Src/mpu6050.c ****    */
 156:Core/Src/mpu6050.c ****   if (!mpu->is_calibrated)
